ED_Title: Administrative and budgetary coordination of the United Nations with the specialized agencies and the International Atomic Energy Agency
ED_DecisionText: At its 55th (resumed) plenary meeting, on 24 December 2024, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Fifth Committee. (Footnote: A/79/647.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/79/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
